<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Parabéns Enviado</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tailwindcss@2.2.19/dist/tailwind.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body class="bg-gradient-to-br from-yellow-100 via-pink-100 to-red-100 flex items-center justify-center min-h-screen">
  <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-2xl text-center max-w-md border border-yellow-200">
    <!-- Imagem realista de bolo -->
    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1565958011703-44f9829ba187?auto=format&fit=crop&w=400&q=80" alt="Bolo de Aniversário" class="w-40 h-40 mx-auto mb-6 rounded-full object-cover shadow-md" />

    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-pink-600 mb-4">🎉 Parabéns Enviado!</h1>

    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4 text-lg">
      A mensagem de parabéns foi enviada com alegria para <strong><%= membro.nome %></strong>!
    </p>

    <a href="/dashboard" class="inline-block bg-pink-500 hover:bg-pink-600 text-white font-semibold px-6 py-2 rounded-lg transition">
      Voltar ao Dashboard
    </a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>

